amic-holographic-display-with-addressable-on-chip-metasurface-network-based-on-lithium-niobate-photonics</link><description>JI，J.，Ye，Z.，Wang，Z。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/dynamic-holographic-display-with-addressable-on-chip-metasurface-network-based-on-lithium-niobate-photonics.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Sep 2025 22:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/09/dynamic-holographic-display-with-addressable-on-chip-metasurface-network-based-on-lithium-niobate-photonics</guid></item></channel></rss>